#CHIP YM2151
#CLOCK 3579545

; YM2151 LFO Test — Testing Low-Frequency Oscillator modulation
;
; The YM2151 includes a built-in LFO that can modulate:
; - Amplitude (tremolo)
; - Frequency (vibrato)
;
; Tests:
; 1. LFO with tremolo (amplitude modulation)
; 2. LFO with vibrato (frequency modulation)
; 3. Different LFO speeds (fast, medium, slow)
; 4. Combined amplitude + frequency modulation

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; LFO at slow speed with tremolo modulation
; Playing steady note with amplitude modulation
c4 . . . .

r4

; LFO at medium speed with vibrato (frequency modulation)
c4 . . . .

r4

; LFO at fast speed with vibrato
c4 . . . .

r4

; Combined tremolo + vibrato
c4 . . . .

r4

; LFO sweep (variable speed)
c4 . . . .

r4

; Hold for LFO effects to settle
r2

#END
